      "content": "idk what u mean by letting myself go. do u mean like just being lazy? because it feels heavier than that. it feels like there's this massive weight of being nothing, and every day is just... performing being a person. it's so exhausting to pretend that any of this matters when it really doesn't. it's almost like the most honest thing to do would be to just stop trying to exist in this way.",
